### 10. HOW CAN YOU REVIEW, UPDATE, OR DELETE THE DATA WE COLLECT FROM YOU?

Based on the applicable laws of your country, you may have the right to request access to the personal information we collect from you, details about how we process it, and correct inaccuracies or request its deletion. To request to review, update, or delete your personal information, please fill out and submit a data subject access request.

